name: Ramen Ratings
content:
Description: data about over 4000 varieties of ramen, as of April 2022.

Source: [The Ramen Rater](https://www.theramenrater.com/resources-2/the-list/)

Columns:

* Brand (string): Brand of the ramen
* Variety (string): The ramen variety, eg a flavor, style, ingredient
* Style (string): Style of container (cup, pack, or tray)
* Country (string): Origin country of the ramen brand
* Stars (numerical): 0-5 rating of the ramen, 5 is best, 0 is worst
